    "chunk_id": "docling_scihub_s11661-013-1726-7.pdf_2_0",
    "text": "Fig. 2-Microstructures of alloy B in (a) as-cast and (b) SHTed (8 h) conditions; and EBSD results of (c) a-Fe in (b) and (d) STed -Fe in (b).",
